  "texts": [
    "These issues primarily include a failure to accurately understand the question, leading to difficulty in mapping the question to the available information.",
    "Additionally, LLMs struggle to effectively apply the cues in the question to narrow down the relevant entities.",
    "They also often fail to apply specific constraints that logically limit the search space.",
    "Generally, LLMs have difficulty grasping specifics such as temporal context, aggregating or summarizing answers, and disambiguating among multiple choices.",
    "Furthermore, they frequently choose incorrect relations, particularly in complex queries requiring multi-hop reasoning, finding it challenging to focus on the relevant elements necessary to formulate an answer."
  ],
